#' Plot a multimod_ast as a visNetwork interactive graph #' #' @param x A multimod_ast object #' @param ... Unused #' @export plot.multimod_ast <- function(x, ...) nodes <- list() edges <- list() node_id_counter <- 0 id_map <- list() # Prevent duplicate nodes plot_d.multimod_ast(x, ...) add_node <- function(label, group) key <- paste0(group, "::", label) if (!key %in% names(id_map)) node_id_counter <<- node_id_counter + 1 id_map[key] <<- node_id_counter nodes[length(nodes) + 1] <<- data.frame(id = node_id_counter, label = label, group = group, stringsAsFactors = FALSE) return(id_map[key])
